{"tid":1257061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"升級？點樣升級好？","createTime":"2019-06-25T10:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T11:05:43.000Z","uid":25431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9ab14acc6b15856e27168ede6faebdcedca2d3","tid":1257061,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"如果以n年一遇嘅G20+政治風波<br />\n只要求撤回<br />\n我會覺得太可惜 點解我哋永遠都係比人打到埋牆角先識反擊？<br />\n點解唔好好借呢次機會 爭取我哋應得嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">普選</span></span></strong><br />\n免除日後比人打埋牆角嘅機會呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家要食住個勢 提出更有利香港日後發展嘅要求<br />\n咁先叫升級㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家暫時民意大好 加埋後生仔做街站<br />\n其實教育大眾都唔係難事<br />\n仲有機會r埋班淺藍嘅民意<br />\n<br />\n而且以普世價值+基本法本身有承諾過普選呢件事 同國際講<br />\n可以攞到更多關注<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話我哋要放棄之前嘅四點訴求<br />\n而係開拓更重要嘅第五訴求<br />\n林奠落完台 又派返個中共党員管我哋 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望喺向G20請願同國際公開信入面 都可以加入我哋嘅第五訴求：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">普選</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d3a11d152b19a699a2b8194c5bf8e9fe72340da1","tid":1257061,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:55:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"98da39034e33ce2f76f55c7cc6dcffe05c4a95e2","tid":1257061,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fe48916c0ee0f37b846143a085d3705cb238ad07","tid":1257061,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:56:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e2915f32e6018f335941ea615dafde9af55fef3a","tid":1257061,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bb28ed17258c42b86604bf397cee69b8f4b830b6","tid":1257061,"uid":200801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9e52bda75d0397495a8d7